INSERT INTO `MailTemplate` VALUES (98,"","","","","","","","","","","","","","","","",16712188,"It took much time to translate the high chief\\'s text. I was dismayed by what I found. High Chief Winterfall was in an extreme state of paranoia in his last days and was addicted to a substance he called \\"firewater.\\" He believed that all creatures were his enemies. Well, I will let you read it for yourself -- I have included a translation of his words with this letter. If you are ever in need, please visit me again.","","","","","","","","","","","","","","","",16712190); 
