INSERT INTO `MailTemplate` VALUES (101,"","","","","","","","","","","","","","","","",16712188,"My friend - though my arm is weary from the battle we continue to wage in the Plaguelands, it is always strong enough to pen this missive to a hero such as you.  It pleases me to know the aid you rendered us continues to yield benefits, ones we try to enact upon on a daily basis.
INSERT INTO `MailTemplate` VALUES (102,"","","","","","","","","","","","","","","","",16712188,"Ho Ho Hello, $N!  I hope you have a fantastic Feast of Winter Veil!$B$BYou were so nice in helping me out with my sweet tooth, that I wanted to send you a little something extra.  It\\'s a sampler of delicious Smokywood Pastures treats.  If you haven\\'t gotten any yet, be sure to do so before the season ends!$B$BSeasons Greetings...$BGreatfather Winter","","","","","","","","","","","","","","","",16712190); 
